[[File:Djmaul.jpg|thumb|200px|Tommy Mac aka DJ Maul.]]
'''Tommy Mac''' wrote the backstory of [[Cebann Veekan]] appearing in the [[Databank (original)|Databank]], through the ''[[What's The Story?]]'' feature of [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]].

He goes by the alias of ''DJ Maul: Got Feet?'' and has a long running Virtual Toy Room Tour blog on [[StarWars.com]]. He is a Mobile Disc Jockey, and has an entire room in his basement dedicated to his ever growing Star Wars collection. He attended Celebration 3 in 2005 dressed as "Darth Vader In A Tux" and was the organizer for Celebration IV's "Official Star Wars Bloggers Meet & Greet Party."<ref name="Blog">{{Blog|DJMaul|127|C4 Recap: The Bloggers Meet & Greet Party!}}</ref>

